{
  "text": "Could you tell me why it is important for the appurtenances and other things to be so carefully aligned with respect to the instrument and why just a small ruffle in the sheet by the instrument causes a problem with the reception of Ra? I am Ra. We may attempt an explanation. This contact is narrow-band. The instrument is highly sensitive. Thus we have good entry into it and can use it to an increasingly satisfactory level. However, the trance condition is, shall we say, not one which is without toll upon this instrument. Therefore, the area above the entrance into the physical complex of this instrument must be kept clear to avoid discomfort to the instrument especially as it re-enters the body complex. The appurtenances give to the instrument sensory input and mental visualization which aid in the trance beginning. The careful alignment of these is important for the energizing group in that it is a reminder to that support group that it is time for a working. The ritualistic behaviors are triggers for many energies of the support group. You may have noticed more energy being used in workings as the number has increased due to the long-term, shall we say, effect of such ritualistic actions. This would not aid another group as it was designed for this particular system of mind/body/spirit complexes and especially the instrument. There is enough energy transferred for one more long query. We do not wish to deplete this instrument.",
  "timestamps": {
    "segment": [
      {
        "segment": "Could you tell me why it is important for the appurtenances and other things to be so carefully aligned with respect to the instrument and why just a small ruffle in the sheet by the instrument causes a problem with the reception of Ra?",
        "start_offset": 0,
        "end_offset": 236,
        "start": 0.0,
        "end": 20.42
      },
      {
        "segment": "I am Ra.",
        "start_offset": 237,
        "end_offset": 245,
        "start": 20.48,
        "end": 21.5
      },
      {
        "segment": "We may attempt an explanation.",
        "start_offset": 246,
        "end_offset": 276,
        "start": 21.52,
        "end": 27.801
      },
      {
        "segment": "This contact is narrow-band.",
        "start_offset": 277,
        "end_offset": 305,
        "start": 30.101,
        "end": 36.561
      },
      {
        "segment": "The instrument is highly sensitive.",
        "start_offset": 306,
        "end_offset": 341,
        "start": 38.101,
        "end": 46.541
      },
      {
        "segment": "Thus we have good entry into it and can use it to an increasingly satisfactory level.",
        "start_offset": 342,
        "end_offset": 427,
        "start": 47.761,
        "end": 70.622
      },
      {
        "segment": "However, the trance condition is, shall we say, not one which is without toll upon this instrument.",
        "start_offset": 428,
        "end_offset": 527,
        "start": 72.462,
        "end": 97.842
      },
      {
        "segment": "Therefore, the area above the entrance into the physical complex of this instrument must be kept clear to avoid discomfort to the instrument especially as it re-enters the body complex.",
        "start_offset": 528,
        "end_offset": 713,
        "start": 100.202,
        "end": 145.943
      },
      {
        "segment": "The appurtenances give to the instrument sensory input and mental visualization which aid in the trance beginning.",
        "start_offset": 714,
        "end_offset": 828,
        "start": 147.323,
        "end": 175.144
      },
      {
        "segment": "The careful alignment of these is important for the energizing group in that it is a reminder to that support group that it is time for a working.",
        "start_offset": 829,
        "end_offset": 975,
        "start": 176.964,
        "end": 216.445
      },
      {
        "segment": "The ritualistic behaviors are triggers for many energies of the support group.",
        "start_offset": 976,
        "end_offset": 1054,
        "start": 217.625,
        "end": 235.185
      },
      {
        "segment": "You may have noticed more energy being used in workings as the number has increased due to the long-term, shall we say, effect of such ritualistic actions.",
        "start_offset": 1055,
        "end_offset": 1210,
        "start": 236.985,
        "end": 273.086
      },
      {
        "segment": "This would not aid another group as it was designed for this particular system of mind/body/spirit complexes and especially the instrument.",
        "start_offset": 1211,
        "end_offset": 1350,
        "start": 276.606,
        "end": 309.187
      },
      {
        "segment": "There is enough energy transferred for one more long query.",
        "start_offset": 1351,
        "end_offset": 1410,
        "start": 311.047,
        "end": 323.328
      },
      {
        "segment": "We do not wish to deplete this instrument.",
        "start_offset": 1411,
        "end_offset": 1453,
        "start": 324.268,
        "end": 333.548
      }
    ],
